Dear <%= @contact[:name] %>,

<%= @trip[:user][:name] %> started their <%= @trip[:name] %> trip on <%= @trip[:startDate] %> at <%= @trip[:startTime] %> and has not checked in.

Here is all the information they recorded about their trip:

Trip starting point: <%= @trip[:startingPoint]%>
Trip ending point: <%= @trip[:endingPoint]%>
<% unless @trip[:travelingCompanions].nil? %> Number of traveling companions: <%= @trip[:travelingCompanions] %>
<% end %>


Gear they have with them:
<% if !@trip[:tripGears].nil? %>
  <% @trip[:tripGears].map do |gear| %>
  <div class="gear">
    Item name: <%= gear[:gear][0] if not nil? %>
    Description: <%= gear[:gear][1] if not nil? %>
    Comments: <%= gear[:comments] if not nil? %>
  </div>
  <% end %>
<% end %>


Vehicle description:
<% unless @trip[:vehicle][:make].nil? %>Make: <%= @trip[:vehicle][:make] %> <% end %>
<% unless @trip[:vehicle][:model].nil? %>Model: <%= @trip[:vehicle][:model] %> <% end %>
<% unless @trip[:vehicle][:year].nil? %>Year: <%= @trip[:vehicle][:year] %> <% end %>
<% unless @trip[:vehicle][:color].nil? %>Color: <%= @trip[:vehicle][:color] %> <% end %>
<% unless @trip[:vehicle][:licensePlate].nil? %>License plate: <%= @trip[:vehicle][:licensePlate] %> <% end %>
<% unless @trip[:vehicle][:state].nil? %>License plate state: <%= @trip[:vehicle][:state] %> <% end %>


Physical description:
<% unless @trip[:user][:name].nil? %>Name: <%= @trip[:user][:name] %> <% end %>
<% unless @trip[:user][:birthDate].nil? %>Birth date: <%= @trip[:user][:birthDate] %> <% end %>
<% unless @trip[:user][:allergies].nil? %>Allergies: <%= @trip[:user][:allergies] %> <% end %>
<% unless @trip[:user][:weight].nil? %>Weight: <%= @trip[:user][:weight] %> <% end %>
<% unless @trip[:user][:height].nil? %>Height: <%= @trip[:user][:height] %> <% end %>
<% unless @trip[:user][:hairColor].nil? %>Hair color: <%= @trip[:user][:hairColor] %> <% end %>
<% unless @trip[:user][:experienceLevel].nil? %>Experience level: <%= @trip[:user][:experienceLevel] %> <% end %>
<% unless @trip[:user][:cosarCard].nil? %>Colorado Search & Rescue Card?: <%= @trip[:user][:cosarCard] %> <% end %>


Please contact a nearby search and rescue team below:
<% @trip[:nearbySarTeams].map do |team| %>
  <div class="teams">
    Team name: <%= team[:teamName ]%>
    County: <%= team[:county] %>
    Contact: <%= team[:contact] %>
    Contact number: <%= team[:contactNumber] %>
    City: <%= team[:city] %>
    State: <%= team[:state] %>
  </div>
<% end %>
